WEBVTT

00:01.000 --> 00:02.298
<i>Previously on</i> One Tree Hill:

00:02.369 --> 00:03.495
Do I know you?

00:03.570 --> 00:05.060
You should. I'm your sister-in-law.

00:05.138 --> 00:07.436
We agreed to keep
what happened between us a secret.

00:07.507 --> 00:09.372
Relax, Nathan. Haley doesn't have a clue.

00:09.442 --> 00:11.637
Jenny's mine now. Hand her over.

00:11.711 --> 00:12.939
Forget it.

00:13.013 --> 00:15.379
The rumors. They weren't rumors.

00:15.915 --> 00:17.109
I'm gay.

00:17.183 --> 00:19.413
This is all my stuff. I don't understand.

00:19.486 --> 00:21.420
I had my mom talk to your parents...

00:21.488 --> 00:24.082
and they said that you could stay here
till the summer.

00:24.157 --> 00:26.557
Thank you, Karen.
You know you saved my life, right?

00:26.626 --> 00:28.218
I'm not gonna make it easy on you...

00:28.294 --> 00:31.286
and sometimes
you're not gonna like me for it.

00:32.265 --> 00:34.324
It's just like having a real mom.

